    <p style="margin-top: 0;color: #565656;font-family: Georgia,serif;font-size: 120%;line-height: 1.2;margin-bottom: 25px">Hi, Alex,</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 0;color: #565656;font-family: Georgia,serif;font-size: 120%;line-height: 1.2;margin-bottom: 25px">Cron job report here!</p>
    <ul>
        <li style="margin-top: 0;color: #565656;font-family: Georgia,serif;font-size: 120%;line-height: 1.2;margin-bottom: 15px">
